00:43:13.994 --> 00:43:17.498
Gospod Bonanos, ali lahko
na hitro govorimo z vami?

00:43:32.846 --> 00:43:34.848
Jake.

00:43:36.016 --> 00:43:41.522
Kako si, Jake?
